Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.gef.graph.Graph

    public final class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.eclipse.gef.common.attributes.IAttributeStore
    A Graph is a container for Nodes and Edges between those Nodes.
